{"id": 237093448, "title": "Ondo varsity student hangs self outside campus", "text": "A student of the Adekunle Ajasin University, Akungba Akoko, Modupe Ayandare, was found dead outside the campus of the university on Monday. Ayandare, who was in the 500 level of the Department of Agronomy of the institution, was found hanged beside the church she attended, which is located off-campus of the state government-owned institution. PUNCH Metro gathered that the deceased went to a vigil at her church but left the church in the early hours of Monday to hang herself beside the church. However, the reason for the action had not been revealed as of the time of filing this report. Confirming the incident, the Public Relations Officer of the Students Union Government of the university, Comrade Olaogbebikan Noble, in a statement, said all hands were on deck to unravel the cause of the incident. The statement read, \u201cWe express in strong terms our dissatisfaction and agony with respect to the death of one of our students, Ayandare Modupe, a 500l student of the Department of Agronomy (Agronomy departmental president). \u201cAccording to a report, the deceased was said to have committed suicide in the early hours of today (Monday) around 4 am after they finished a vigil in her church. The incident happened beside the church she attended around Sportless Villa. \u201cThe law enforcement agency has been informed already and all hands are on desk in getting to the root of the situation. Rest assured justice will be served and the law enforcement agency will do a thorough investigation. Should you have any information to supply regarding the incident that happened, kindly reach out to the Students\u2019 Union. Stay tuned for further updates as further investigations are underway.\u201d The state Police Public Relations Officer, Mrs Funmilayo Odunlami, who confirmed the incident, told our correspondent that the command was working around the clock to unravel the cause of the incident. \u201cYes, we got the information. And the police are working very hard to unravel the circumstances surrounding the incident,\u201d she said.", "summary": "<p>A student of the Adekunle Ajasin University, Akungba Akoko, Modupe Ayandare, was found dead outside the campus of the university on Monday. Ayandare, who was in the 500 level of the Department of Agronomy of the institution, was found hanged beside the church she attended, which is located off-campus of the state government-owned institution. PUNCH </p>\n <br/> <a href='https://punchng.com/ondo-varsity-student-hangs-self-outside-campus/'>Read More</a>", "url": "https://punchng.com/ondo-varsity-student-hangs-self-outside-campus/", "image": "https://cdn.punchng.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01180925/Adekunle-Ajasin-University-Akungba-Akoko-e1564679390107.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-18 01:10:49", "author": "Peter Dada", "authors": ["Peter Dada"], "language": "en", "catgory": "politics", "source_country": "ng", "sentiment": -0.496}